</span>
</span></p><p>At this point, your artichoke will have a flat top with a few rows of pointy leaves around the sides.</p><p>
<span
class="pibfi_pinterest ">
<img
class="alignnone wp-image-56355 size-full" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPScxMTYwJyBoZWlnaHQ9JzExNTUnPjwvc3ZnPg==" data-original=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes.jpg alt="Hands rubbing artichoke with lemon" width=1160 height=1155 data-pin-description="Learn how to cook artichokes perfectly every time! This simple steamed artichokes recipe is a delicious, healthy spring appetizer. Serve the tender leaves with a tasty sauce or melted butter for dipping! | Love and Lemons #artichoke #spring #appetizers #healthy" data-srcset="https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes.jpg 1160w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes-150x150.jpg 150w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes-300x300.jpg 300w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes-1024x1020.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes-282x282.jpg 282w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes-100x100.jpg 100w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes-158x158.jpg 158w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes-580x578.jpg 580w" sizes="(max-width: 1160px) 100vw, 1160px" data-pin-url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/how-to-cook-artichokes/ >
<span
class=xc_pin onclick="pin_this(event, 'http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/how-to-cook-artichokes/&media=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-prepare-artichokes.jpg&description=Learn+how+to+cook+artichokes+perfectly+every+time%21+This+simple+steamed+artichokes+recipe+is+a+delicious%2C+healthy+spring+appetizer.+Serve+the+tender+leaves+with+a+tasty+sauce+or+melted+butter+for+dipping%21+%7C+Love+and+Lemons+%23artichoke+%23spring+%23appetizers+%23healthy')">
</span>
</span></p><p>Rub the cut, flat leaves liberally with lemon juice&#8230;</p><p>
<span
class="pibfi_pinterest ">
<img
class="alignnone wp-image-56352 size-full" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPScxMTYwJyBoZWlnaHQ9JzEyNjMnPjwvc3ZnPg==" data-original=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-cook-artichokes-2.jpg alt="Hands trimming thorny artichoke petals with kitchen shears" width=1160 height=1263 data-pin-description="Learn how to cook artichokes perfectly every time! This simple steamed artichokes recipe is a delicious, healthy spring appetizer. Serve the tender leaves with a tasty sauce or melted butter for dipping! | Love and Lemons #artichoke #spring #appetizers #healthy" data-srcset="https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-cook-artichokes-2.jpg 1160w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-cook-artichokes-2-276x300.jpg 276w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-cook-artichokes-2-940x1024.jpg 940w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-cook-artichokes-2-92x100.jpg 92w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-cook-artichokes-2-580x632.jpg 580w" sizes="(max-width: 1160px) 100vw, 1160px" data-pin-url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/how-to-cook-artichokes/ >
<span
class=xc_pin onclick="pin_this(event, 'http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/how-to-cook-artichokes/&media=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/how-to-cook-artichokes-2.jpg&description=Learn+how+to+cook+artichokes+perfectly+every+time%21+This+simple+steamed+artichokes+recipe+is+a+delicious%2C+healthy+spring+appetizer.+Serve+the+tender+leaves+with+a+tasty+sauce+or+melted+butter+for+dipping%21+%7C+Love+and+Lemons+%23artichoke+%23spring+%23appetizers+%23healthy')">
</span>
</span></p><p>and use kitchen shears to trim off the pointy tips of the lower leaves. (Fun fact: artichokes are the flower buds of a member of the thistle family. From those prickly leaves, you can tell!)</p><p>It&#8217;s time to cook!</p><p>
<span
class="pibfi_pinterest ">
<img
class="alignnone wp-image-56359 size-full" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0naHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmcnIHdpZHRoPScxMTYwJyBoZWlnaHQ9JzExMDYnPjwvc3ZnPg==" data-original=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/artichoke-2.jpg alt="How to cook artichokes - artichokes in steamer basket" width=1160 height=1106 data-pin-description="Learn how to cook artichokes perfectly every time! This simple steamed artichokes recipe is a delicious, healthy spring appetizer. Serve the tender leaves with a tasty sauce or melted butter for dipping! | Love and Lemons #artichoke #spring #appetizers #healthy" data-srcset="https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/artichoke-2.jpg 1160w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/artichoke-2-300x286.jpg 300w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/artichoke-2-1024x976.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/artichoke-2-100x95.jpg 100w, https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/artichoke-2-580x553.jpg 580w" sizes="(max-width: 1160px) 100vw, 1160px" data-pin-url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/how-to-cook-artichokes/ >
<span
class=xc_pin onclick="pin_this(event, 'http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://www.loveandlemons.com/how-to-cook-artichokes/&media=https://cdn.loveandlemons.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/artichoke-2.jpg&description=Learn+how+to+cook+artichokes+perfectly+every+time%21+This+simple+steamed+artichokes+recipe+is+a+delicious%2C+healthy+spring+appetizer.+Serve+the+tender+leaves+with+a+tasty+sauce+or+melted+butter+for+dipping%21+%7C+Love+and+Lemons+%23artichoke+%23spring+%23appetizers+%23healthy')">
</span>
</span></p><h2>How to Cook Artichokes</h2><p>My go-to method for how to cook artichokes is to steam them. Steaming artichokes is easy and hands-off, and it&#8217;s a perfect way to prepare them if you want to peel off the leaves and dip them in a sauce or melted butter.</p><p>Once you&#8217;ve prepared the artichoke, add 1 inch of cold water to a large pot, and squeeze in any juice remaining in your lemon. Drop the juiced lemon segments into the water, too. Place a steamer basket inside the pot, and nestle in the artichoke. Bring to a boil over high heat. Then, reduce the heat to a simmer. Cover and cook for 35-45 minutes.</p><p>The artichoke is ready when the stem is fork-tender and you can easily peel away the outer leaves.</p><p>
